      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Organizations\" title=\"Organizations\">Organizations</a> * Institute of Theoretical and Experimental Physics</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:Cheremushki_Estate_Flickr_06.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d0/Cheremushki_Estate_Flickr_06.jpg/330px-Cheremushki_Estate_Flickr_06.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d0/Cheremushki_Estate_Flickr_06.jpg/500px-Cheremushki_Estate_Flickr_06.jpg 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d0/Cheremushki_Estate_Flickr_06.jpg/960px-Cheremushki_Estate_Flickr_06.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Cheremushki_Estate_Flickr_06.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>ITEP <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>ITEP</b>, <br />\nthe Institute of Theoretical and Experimental Physics (ITEP or ITEF), located in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Moscow\">Moscow</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Russia\">Russia</a>, established  in 1945 <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. The main fields of research include <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Theoretical_physics\">theoretical</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mathematical_physics\">mathematical physics</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Astrophysics\">astrophysics</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Particle_physics\">elementary particle physics</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nuclear_physics\">nuclear physics</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Plasma_%28physics%29\">plasma physics</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Solid-state_physics\">solid-state physics</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nanotechnology\">nanotechnologies</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nuclear_reactor\">reactor</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Particle_accelerator\">accelerator</a> technoligies, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Medical_physics\">medical physics</a>, and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Computer_science\">computer science</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#People\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">People</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Chess_Program\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chess Program</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Matches\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Matches</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Photos\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Photos</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"People\">People</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Institute_of_Theoretical_and_Experimental_Physics&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: People\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Georgy_Adelson-Velsky\" title=\"Georgy Adelson-Velsky\">Georgy Adelson-Velsky</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Vladimir_Arlazarov\" title=\"Vladimir Arlazarov\">Vladimir Arlazarov</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Alexander_Bitman\" title=\"Alexander Bitman\">Alexander Bitman</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Alexander_Brudno\" title=\"Alexander Brudno\">Alexander Brudno</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mikhail_Donskoy\" title=\"Mikhail Donskoy\">Mikhail Donskoy</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Alexander_Kronrod\" title=\"Alexander Kronrod\">Alexander Kronrod</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Anatoly_Uskov\" title=\"Anatoly Uskov\">Anatoly Uskov</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Alexander_Zhivotovsky\" title=\"Alexander Zhivotovsky\">Alexander Zhivotovsky</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chess_Program\">Chess Program</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Institute_of_Theoretical_and_Experimental_Physics&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Chess Program\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/ITEP_Chess_Program\" title=\"ITEP Chess Program\">ITEP Chess Program</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Matches\">Matches</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Institute_of_Theoretical_and_Experimental_Physics&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Matches\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Stanford-ITEP_Match\" title=\"Stanford-ITEP Match\">Stanford-ITEP Match</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Photos\">Photos</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Institute_of_Theoretical_and_Experimental_Physics&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Photos\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/ITEP_Chess_Program#Video\" title=\"ITEP Chess Program#Video\"><img alt=\"ItepTeamTV.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/8f/ItepTeamTV.jpg/800px-ItepTeamTV.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"529\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" srcset=\"/images/8/8f/ItepTeamTV.jpg 1.5x\" /></a></div> \n<p><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">ITEP</a> team during TV interview, November 24, 1967, <a href=\"/M-20\" title=\"M-20\">M-20</a> in the background, from left:<br />\n<a href=\"/Anatoly_Uskov\" title=\"Anatoly Uskov\">Anatoly Uskov</a>, <a href=\"/Georgy_Adelson-Velsky\" title=\"Georgy Adelson-Velsky\">Georgy Adelson-Velsky</a>, interviewer, <a href=\"/Alexander_Bitman\" title=\"Alexander Bitman\">Alexander Bitman</a>, <a href=\"/Vladimir_Arlazarov\" title=\"Vladimir Arlazarov\">Vladimir Arlazarov</a> and <a href=\"/Alexander_Zhivotovsky\" title=\"Alexander Zhivotovsky\">Alexander Zhivotovsky</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Institute_of_Theoretical_and_Experimental_Physics&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.itep.ru/\">ITEP official side</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Institute_for_Theoretical_and_Experimental_Physics\">Institute of Theoretical and Experimental Physics from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://7iskusstv.com/2014/Nomer2_3/Lapidus1.php\">Memories of ITEP</a> (in Russian)</li>\n<li> <span id=\"Video\"></span>1961. Moscow. ITEP</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <div class='embedvideo ev_inline ev_top autoResize' style=' width: 646px;'><div class='embedvideowrap' style='width: 640px;'><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/T06vZQjf_98?\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe></div></div></dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Institute_of_Theoretical_and_Experimental_Physics&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/lotzman/1025419538/\">Cheremushki manor (ITEP), Palace</a>, by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/lotzman/\">Lotzman Katzman</a> August 05, 2007, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Institute_for_Theoretical_and_Experimental_Physics\">Institute of Theoretical and Experimental Physics from Wikipedia</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikimedia_Commons\">Wikimedia Commons</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Institute_for_Theoretical_and_Experimental_Physics\">Institute of Theoretical and Experimental Physics from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.itep.ru/eng/\">ITEP official side</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Image captured from the <a href=\"/ITEP_Chess_Program#Video\" title=\"ITEP Chess Program\">Video В шахматы \"играет\" ЭВМ. Телевизионные новости. Эфир 24.11.1967</a>, 3:03</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/Organizations\" title=\"Organizations\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228101309\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.069 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.611 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 89/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 208/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 26/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:2231-0!canonical and timestamp 20260228101309 and revision id 25555\n -->\n"
